Project Description
"Google Analytic Dashboard Controls" is costume control library which contain ASP.NET costume controls which generate different types of charts using Google analytic data export api.

Its include following controls.

1. Visitors overviews
2. Word map overview
3. Traffic source overview
4. Content overview

Also have helper class which have methods like
  • getTrackerCode() - to get the tracker code to put into your page.
  • getProfilesList() - to get list of profile into your analytic account.

For more information go through this link
http://jigneshsuvariya.blogspot.com/2010/01/google-analytic-dashboard-controls.html
